{
  "stem": "523.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two girls-- one was 15, one was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And each time when the Germans came in, they used to lie down on the floor and take the younger children to sit on top of them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later, I find out they were afraid that they will be raped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After those two Germans left our room, they came along the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a mother with a little girl, a little boy, a baby wrapped up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They shot the mother of the child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Blood was pouring on the streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two days later, the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the streets were filled with blood of Jewish people and Jewish children, dead people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wouldn't allow to bury the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made movies about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But does anybody see them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We automatically became solid citizen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't children, Jewish children, survivors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were Soviet citizen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used us for propaganda to show they liberated Soviet citizen from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was no mentioning we were Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- and also, I forgot to mention, after when those two Germans left, we decided-- it might sound funny-- we are going to fight.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are talking children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How are we going to fight?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the night, we are going to pick up some stones and keep the-- there was like a attic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the older boys was 15, 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the two girls will hide in the attic up there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now the smaller children will give them stones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the German will come back, they will throw the stones from up there-- beautiful, beautiful fighting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were lucky they never came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because if somebody come back and we throw stones, I wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
